Node "Jack_townhall4"
notes ""
{
NPCText "*he leans back* I know it's a big job, but I think you're the best one to do it. And you'll have the gratitude of this whole town if you pull it off. Let me know when you're ready for the meeting. "
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'll be back when I'm ready." linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm ready now (fadeout to town hall)" linkto "Jack_townhall5"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jack_townhall5"
notes "After the meeting (assuming success)..."
{
NPCText "*Jack looks ten years younger* You did it! Hot damn, now I can start retiring. All of Crossroads owes you, <PC>, and don't think they won't remember it. As for me ... well, hell, now that you've freed me up, I shouldn't need this darling anymore. *he hands you his .223 pistol* She got me through a lot of tight spots over the years, and I trust she'll do the same for you. Thanks again, friend."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Thanks, Jack! Be seeing you." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jack_happy"
notes ""
{
NPCText "*Jack smiles* Good to see you, <PC>. What can I do for you?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Hi Jack, got any more work?" linkto "Jack_happy2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'd like to know more about you, Jack." linkto "Jack_history"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Could you tell me about Crossroads, Jack?" linkto "Jack_crossroadsyes"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Jack, I need to talk to you about the Unified Traders." linkto "Jack_UT"  notes "Only available when the PC has evidence incriminating the UT."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Jack, I need to talk to you about Brahmin rustling." linkto "Jack_rustling"  notes "Only available if the PC has talked to Brahmin farmers about the rustling (if we even want to include this)."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Just stopping by to say hi, Jack." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jack_happy2"
notes ""
{
NPCText "*he chuckles* I'm retiring, remember. Check with Warren."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Okay. Say, I'd like to hear more about you." linkto "Jack_history"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Okay. Would you mind telling me about Crossroads?" linkto "Jack_crossroadsyes"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "All right, I'll do that. See you later, Jack." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jack_history"
notes ""
{
NPCText "*he blinks* Me? Well, ah, there's not much to tell. Grew up on a Lone Star ranch, took over when the old man died, ran Brahmin for  many years, then brought my family here fifteen years ago and set up Crossroads."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What can you tell me about the town?" linkto "Jack_crossroadsyes"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What made you leave Lone Star?" linkto "Jack_history2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me about your family." linkto "Jack_family"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me about your travels." linkto "Jack_travels"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jack_crossroadsyes"
notes ""
{
NPCText "What do you want to know? Fifteen years ago I set up this town, and blah blah blah. I'll have more to say when my dialogue writer does more work."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Okay." linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can you tell me about your family?" linkto "Jack_family"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can you tell me about your travels?" linkto "Jack_travels"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jack_history2"
notes ""
{
NPCText "*he sighs* Well, there a few reasons. The deathclaw attacks were getting worse, my landlord was getting greedy, and my wife died. Felt like I needed a change after that.  "
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What's a deathclaw?" linkto "Jack_deathclaw"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "May I ask about your wife?" linkto "Jack_wife"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can you tell me about Crossroads?" linkto "Jack_crossroadsyes"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Bye" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jack_family"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Family? It's just me and my boys, Lawrence and Warren. My wife Meg died years ago."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "May I ask about Meg?" linkto "Jack_wife"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me about Lawrence." linkto "Jack_lawrence"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me about Warren." linkto "Jack_warren"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "That's it for now. Seeya." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jack_travels"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Oh, I've been all over. When my dialogue writer does more work, I'll tell you about it."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can you tell me about your family?" linkto "Jack_family"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can you tell me about the town?" linkto "Jack_crossroadsyes"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Okay." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jack_wife"
notes ""
{
NPCText "*his smile fades* I don't want to talk about her."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Jack, I think it would do you some good to share your feelings." linkto "Jack_wife2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I understand. Can I ask you about Lawrence?" linkto "Jack_lawrence"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I understand. Can I ask you about Warren?" linkto "Jack_warren"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sorry, I'll let you be now. Seeya." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jack_wife2"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Share my feelings?! Just drop it."
 NPCFemaleText "I appreciate the thought, but it'll just open old wounds that took a long time to heal over."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Okay. Can I ask you about Lawrence?" linkto "Jack_lawrence"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Okay. Can I ask you about Warren?" linkto "Jack_warren"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Okay, I'll be seeing you then." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jack_lawrence"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Lawrence? He's my eldest, a tough boy. *he frowns* Too tough in some ways ... anyway, I'm glad he wasn't interested in taking over."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'll ask you about The Club and stuff when the dialogue writer does more work." linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What about Warren?" linkto "Jack_warren"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jack_warren"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Warren?  He's a good boy. * he leans closer* Between you and me, though, he's a bit naive ... I'm glad he won't be filling my shoes. I don't like his association with those Unified Traders."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What can you tell me about the Unified Traders?" linkto "Jack_UT"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What about Lawrence?" linkto "Jack_lawrence"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jack_deathclaw"
notes ""
{
NPCText "You haven't seen a deathclaw yet? Count yourself fortunate then. They're nasty beasts and no mistake."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can you tell me about your family?" linkto "Jack_family"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can you tell me about the town?" linkto "Jack_crossroadsyes"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Bye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jack_UT"
notes ""
{
NPCText "There's something not right with that organization. Can't put my finger on it, but I'll have more to say when the dialogue writer does more work."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I've uncovered evidence that Salvation is pulling the strings behind the UT!" linkto "Jack_UT2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Okay." linkto "done"  notes ""
